---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import ServiceExplore from '../../components/ServiceExplore.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Periodontal Care — Oasis Dental Care, Huntington Beach"
  description="Gentle periodontal care and gum disease treatment in Huntington Beach. Dr. Jason Fu provides deep cleanings and ongoing maintenance. Call (714) 893-2106."
  page="services"
>

<section class="phero">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="crumbs"><a href="/">Home</a><span class="sep">/</span><a href="/services">Services</a><span class="sep">/</span><span style="color:#cfe6e2">Periodontal Care</span></div>
    <span class="tag">Periodontal care</span>
    <h1>Periodontal Care</h1>
    <p>Healthy gums are the foundation of a healthy mouth.</p>
    <div class="acts">
      <a class="btn" href="/contact">Schedule an evaluation <svg class="ico" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6"/></svg></a>
      <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="tel:7148932106">Call (714) 893-2106</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="pad">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="split">
      <div>

        <div class="img-ph reveal">
          <div class="img-ph-ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="3"/><circle cx="8.5" cy="9" r="1.5"/><path d="m21 15-5-5L5 21"/></svg></div>
          <span class="img-ph-lbl">Photo placeholder</span>
          <span class="img-ph-desc">Hygienist working gently with patient in a calm setting</span>
        </div>

        <div class="prose reveal">
          <span class="tag">Overview</span>
          <h2>Protecting the foundation of your smile.</h2>
          <p>We provide gentle, thorough periodontal care—from routine evaluations to deep cleanings and ongoing maintenance—protecting you from gum disease and supporting lifelong oral wellness.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="prose reveal" style="margin-top:48px">
          <h3>What Is Gum Disease?</h3>
          <p>Gum disease (periodontal disease) is a bacterial infection of the gums and supporting bone. It ranges from mild gingivitis (inflammation) to more serious periodontitis, which can lead to tooth loss if left untreated. It's also linked to systemic health issues including heart disease and diabetes.</p>

          <div class="img-ph reveal">
            <div class="img-ph-ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="3"/><circle cx="8.5" cy="9" r="1.5"/><path d="m21 15-5-5L5 21"/></svg></div>
            <span class="img-ph-lbl">Photo placeholder</span>
            <span class="img-ph-desc">Gentle hygienist exam, or clean gum health visual</span>
          </div>

          <h3>Signs of Gum Disease</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Red, swollen, or tender gums</li>
            <li>Bleeding when brushing or flossing</li>
            <li>Receding gumline</li>
            <li>Persistent bad breath</li>
            <li>Loose or shifting teeth</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>What We Offer</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Periodontal evaluations at every visit</li>
            <li>Scaling and root planing (deep cleaning)</li>
            <li>Ongoing periodontal maintenance</li>
            <li>Patient education on home care</li>
          </ul>

          <div class="img-ph reveal">
            <div class="img-ph-ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="3"/><circle cx="8.5" cy="9" r="1.5"/><path d="m21 15-5-5L5 21"/></svg></div>
            <span class="img-ph-lbl">Photo placeholder</span>
            <span class="img-ph-desc">Deep cleaning procedure or patient education moment</span>
          </div>

          <h3>Prevention Is the Goal</h3>
          <p>Catching gum disease early makes treatment simpler and more effective. Regular cleanings, combined with proper home care, are the best defense.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="reveal" style="margin-top:48px">
          <span class="tag">Common questions</span>
          <h2 class="prose" style="margin-top:8px">Good to know.</h2>
          <div class="faq">
            <details open><summary>What is the difference between a regular cleaning and a deep cleaning?</summary><p>A regular cleaning removes plaque and tartar above the gumline. A deep cleaning (scaling and root planing) goes below the gumline to treat active gum disease.</p></details>
            <details><summary>Is gum disease reversible?</summary><p>Early-stage gingivitis is fully reversible with professional treatment and improved home care. More advanced periodontitis can be managed effectively but not completely reversed.</p></details>
            <details><summary>How often do I need periodontal maintenance?</summary><p>Patients with a history of gum disease typically benefit from maintenance visits every 3–4 months instead of the standard 6-month interval.</p></details>
            <details><summary>What can happen if gum disease goes untreated?</summary><p>Untreated gum disease can lead to bone loss, tooth loss, and has been linked to increased risk of heart disease, diabetes complications, and other systemic conditions.</p></details>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <aside>
        <div class="scard reveal">
          <div class="hd"><div class="grid-ov"></div><h3>Schedule a periodontal evaluation</h3><p>Early detection makes treatment simpler</p></div>
          <div class="bd">
            <div class="row"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><path d="M12 7v5l3 2"/></svg><span>Evaluations included at every visit</span></div>
            <div class="row"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg><span>Most insurance accepted &amp; verified</span></div>
            <div class="row"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2 4 5v6c0 5 3.5 9 8 11 4.5-2 8-6 8-11V5l-8-3z"/></svg><span>Gentle, thorough technique</span></div>
            <div class="divider"></div>
            <a class="btn" href="/contact">Schedule a Periodontal Evaluation</a>
            <a class="btn btn-out" href="tel:7148932106" style="justify-content:center">Call (714) 893-2106</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<ServiceExplore />

</Layout>
